<DIV1 TYPE="poem">
<PB REF="341" MS="Y">
<HEAD>Sober Advice from Horace.</HEAD>
<HEAD TYPE="sub">Imitated from his Second Sermon</HEAD>
<LG>
<L>The Tribe of Templars, Play'rs&punc; Apothecaries,</L>
<L>Pimps, Poets, Wits, Lord Fanny's, Lady Mary's,</L>
<L>And all the Court in Tears, and half the Town,</L>
