<L>While bashful Jenny, ev'n at Morning Prayer,</L>
<L><NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">Averse taken from Mr. Pope</NOTE> Spreads her ForeButtocks to the Nawel bare.</L>
<L>But different Taste in diff'rent Men prevails,</L>
<L>And one is fired by Heads, and one by Tails;</L>
<L>Some feel no Flames but at a Court or Ball,</L>
<L>And others hunt white Aprons in the Mall.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>My Lord of Lo&mdash;n, chancing to remark</L>
<L>A noted Dean much busy'd in the Park,</L>
<L>"Proceed (he cry'd) proceed my Reverend Brother</L>
<L>"Tis Fornicatio Simplex, and no other:</L>
<L>"Better than lust for Boys, with Pope and Turk,</L>
<L>"Or others Spouses, like<NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot">Others read Lord-Mayor</NOTE> my Lord of York.</L>
