</DIV1>
<DIV1>
<PB REF="352" MS="Y">
<LG>
<L>Ne$ magis huic, inter niveas viridisque lapillos</L>
<L>Sit licet, o Cerinthe, two tenerum est femur, aut crus</L>
<L>Rectius: atque etiam melius persaepe togataeest.</L>
